summary:
As far as back as I can remember, I’ve always wanted to tell stories. 
I’ve worked in different fields of the film production, contributing with my experience and knowledge to several projects (Film, Television, Advertising) with different crews from diverse nationalities and backgrounds; learning from each of these various work rates and dynamics. 
I’m passionate, patient and persevering, I work hard and learn fast.
